ng\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-3527\" alt=\"Top 10 v1.9.7 - General options\" src=\"http://i0.wp.com/ajaydsouza.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Top-10-v1.9.7-General-options.png?resize=229%2C300\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></a></p>\n<p>And, last week Top 10 crossed 100,000 downloads. Am glad this plugin has received such good acceptance and I thank all of the users of this plugin for this!</p>\n<p>If you&#8217;ve been using Top 10, why not give it a <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/support/view/plugin-reviews/top-10\">5-star review</a>. If you&#8217;re facing issues do use the <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/support/plugin/top-10\">support forums</a> since it is one centralised place that I can easily monitor.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3526\" alt=\"Top 10 - 100k downloads\" src=\"http://i1.wp.com/ajaydsouza.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Top-10-100k.png?resize=183%2C91\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></p>\n</div><hr style=\"border-top:black solid 1px\" /><a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2013/07/04/top-10-v1-9-7-and-100000-downloads/\">Top 10 v1.9.7 and 100,000 downloads</a> was first posted on July 4, 2013 at 8:19 pm.<br />© 2003-2013 \"<a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com\">Ajay - On the Road called Life</a>\". All rights reserved.<br />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2013/07/04/top-10-v1-9-7-and-100000-downloads/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n		